Package edu.upc.essi.dtim

Class Graph

  • java.lang.Object
    • graphJena.edu.upc.essi.dtim.NextiaCore.Graph
  • public class Graph
extends java.lang.Object
    A class that represents a graphJena data structure, where the nodes are represented by instances of the Node class and the edges are represented by instances of the Edge class.
